üü¶ US13 ‚Äì Trigger confirmation modal when clicking NEXT

User Story

As a coach
I want to confirm that I have finished adding equipments before moving on
So that I do not accidentally skip equipment selection

Acceptance Criteria

WHEN at least one equipment is in the Return Summary
AND I click NEXT
THEN a confirmation modal is displayed


