üü¶ US14 ‚Äì Confirmation modal: end of equipment selection

User Story

As a coach
I want to confirm whether I am done adding equipments
So that the process moves safely to the next step

Modal content
	‚Ä¢	Title: Confirmation
	‚Ä¢	Message:
‚ÄúHave you finished adding any material to return?
Next step, you will be able to add accessories.‚Äù
	‚Ä¢	Buttons:
	‚Ä¢	No, I have one ‚Üí return to scanner
	‚Ä¢	Yes, I confirm ‚Üí go to Step 2 (Select accessories)

Acceptance Criteria

